OL,3,CBrothers cleared of murdering couple
OL,4,Cat petrol station in 2003
OL,6,FTwo brothers who spent nearly two
OL,7,Fdecades in prison for a double murder
OL,8,Fhave been cleared after their
OL,9,Fconvictions were overturned and a
OL,10,Fplanned retrial was dropped.
OL,12,FRobert and Lee Firkins were jailed for
OL,13,Fthe November 2003 murders of Carol and
OL,14,FGraham Fisher at their home in Perch,
OL,15,Fnear Wadebridge in Cornwall.
OL,17,FThe brothers denied murder but were
OL,18,Fconvicted and handed life sentences
OL,19,Fwith a minimum term of 26 years in
OL,20,FFebruary 2006.
