OL,6,FBoth men have maintained their
OL,7,Finnocence and unsuccessfully attempted
OL,8,Fto bring an appeal against their
OL,9,Fconvictions in 2008.
OL,11,FBut in 2020 the Criminal Cases Review
OL,12,FCommission (CCRC) referred both
OL,13,Fconvictions to the Court of Appeal,
OL,14,Ffinding there was a "real possibility"
OL,15,Fthat appeal judges could quash their
OL,16,Fconvictions.
OL,18,FAnd in a ruling in December 2023,
OL,19,Fthree judges at the Court of Appeal
OL,20,Fquashed the brothers' convictions,
OL,21,Ffinding them to be "unsafe".
