OL,6,FThe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,7,Fapplied for a retrial for both
OL,8,Fbrothers, meaning that the media could
OL,9,Fnot report their successful appeals.
OL,11,FHowever, at a hearing at Winchester
OL,12,FCrown Court on Monday, the CPS offered
OL,13,Fno evidence against either man.
OL,15,FAnne Whyte KC, for the prosecution,
OL,16,Fsaid there was a "recent difficulty"
OL,17,Fthat may affect the attendance of a
OL,18,Fwitness at the retrial.
