OL,6,FSarah Elliott KC, for Robert Firkins,
OL,7,Ftold the court in June 2023 that there
OL,8,Fwas new expert evidence showing Z to
OL,9,Fbe a "compulsive liar", adding: "It is
OL,10,Fa pathological lying, it is a medical
OL,11,Fcondition."
OL,13,FLord Justice Holroyde, sitting with
OL,14,FLady Justice Thirlwall and Mr Justice
OL,15,FMorris allowed the brothers' appeals.
