OL,6,FSpeaking after the decision to
OL,7,Fdiscontinue the retrial, lawyer Jane
OL,8,FHickman said that the brothers "are
OL,9,Frestored to the innocent status in
OL,10,Frelation to the murders that they had
OL,11,Fat the beginning".
OL,13,FShe added: "The suffering for them has
OL,14,Fbeen immense."
OL,16,FRobert Firkins was due to be released
OL,17,Ffollowing the ruling, while his
OL,18,Fbrother is expected to remain in
OL,19,Fprison due to other offences.
