OL,6,FMs Hickman continued: "I've been
OL,7,Fdealing with appeals for some 40 years
OL,8,Fand I don't think most people realise
OL,9,For recognise the degree of trauma that
OL,10,Fgets inflicted on people who didn't
OL,11,Fcommit a crime but who are punished in
OL,12,Fmind and body day after day after day,
OL,13,Fyear on year."
OL,15,FIn a joint statement Ms Elliott and
OL,16,FJames Wood KC, who represented Lee
OL,17,FFirkins, said: "From the moment of
OL,18,Fthese convictions, we knew the case
OL,19,Fwas a gross miscarriage of justice.
