OL,6,FA spokesperson for Devon and Cornwall
OL,7,FPolice said: "In 2023 the Court of
OL,8,FAppeal overturned the original
OL,9,Fconviction as a result of new medical
OL,10,Fevidence from the Criminal Case Review
OL,11,FCommission.
OL,13,F"Since that point Devon and Cornwall
OL,14,FPolice's Major Crime Investigation
OL,15,FTeam has worked closely with the Crown
OL,16,FProsecution Service (CPS) to prepare
OL,17,Ffor a retrial of Robert and Lee
OL,18,FFirkins scheduled for early 2025.
