OL,6,F"Devon and Cornwall Police understand
OL,7,Fthat whilst the original investigation
OL,8,Fwas over 20 years ago, it is possible
OL,9,Fthat new information exists and so
OL,10,Fanyone who wants to contact ourselves
OL,11,For Crimestoppers, should do so as soon
OL,12,Fas possible."
